  'BarChart3',
  '["Power BI dashboards","Predictive analytics","Data visualization","KPI reporting","BI consulting","Strategic business insights"]'::jsonb,
  0,
  'Data Analytics & Business Intelligence',
  'Transform raw business data into clear dashboards, KPI systems, and strategic insights that help teams make faster and smarter decisions.',
  '["Interactive dashboards for performance tracking","KPI reporting and executive-level decision visibility","Sales, finance, operations, and customer analytics","Data-driven forecasting and business planning"]'::jsonb,
  true,
  'Dashboards, KPI systems, and business intelligence that turn raw data into confident decisions.',
  'Service Overview',
  E'We design analytics systems that connect business goals with measurable data. The result is a clear view of performance, opportunities, risks, and next actions.\n\nOur team can support the full workflow from data preparation and dashboard design to KPI strategy and executive reporting.',
  'Book Free Consultation',
  '/free-services',
  'Contact Us',
  '/contact',
